86
00:03:30,744 --> 00:03:33,078
             Garnet:            
        STEVEN, LET'S GO.       

87
00:03:35,182 --> 00:03:36,815
                Steven: WHOA.   

88
00:03:36,817 --> 00:03:38,183
         HA!                    
