TO TRAVEL ACROSS THE COSMOS     

97
00:03:53,434 --> 00:03:56,101
AND LAND HERE ON EARTH          
BEFORE THE WARP PADS WERE BUILT.

98
00:03:56,103 --> 00:03:57,836
