114
00:04:39,446 --> 00:04:41,213
     PEARL SAYS                 
 YOU'RE THE DULL ONE            

115
00:04:41,215 --> 00:04:43,315
IF YOU THINK YOU CAN FLY        
     THIS WRECK.                

116
