     <i> MESSING WITH MY PLANS,</i>    
     <i> DESTROYING MY THINGS.</i>     

125
00:05:00,501 --> 00:05:03,302
    <i> LOOKS LIKE I'VE GOT YOU</i>    
     <i> JUST WHERE I WANT YOU.</i>    

126
00:05:03,304 --> 00:05:07,072
   <i> HOW DOES IT FEEL TO BE SO</i>   
 <i> EASILY OUTSMARTED, YOU CLODS?!</i>

127
00:05:07,074 --> 00:05:08,173
               NO.              

128
00:05:08,175 --> 00:05:09,975
                 HEY, UH...     
              THIS IS AMETHYST. 

129
00:05:09,977 --> 00:05:11,943
             I DON'T APPRECIATE 
  BEING CALLED A CLOD, YOU CLO--

130
00:05:11,945 --> 00:05:13,345
          <i> ENOUGH TALK.</i>         

131
00:05:13,347 --> 00:05:16,281
       <i> PREPARE YOURSELVES</i>      
       <i> FOR ANNIHILATION!</i>       

132
00:05:16,283 --> 00:05:17,316
             <i> HYAH!</i>             

133
00:05:20,921 --> 00:05:22,087
             <i> HYAH.</i>             

134
00:05:22,089 --> 00:05:24,756
         <i> AHA! IT WORKS.</i>        

135
00:05:24,758 --> 00:05:26,024
              <i> YES!</i>             

136
00:05:26,026 --> 00:05:27,926
 <i> DIE! DIE! DIE! DIE! DIE! DIE!</i> 

137
00:05:27,928 --> 00:05:29,861
<i> DIE! DIE! DIE! DIE! DIE! DIE!</i>  

138
00:05:29,863 --> 00:05:31,930
      HEY, GUYS, OVER HERE.     

139
00:05:33,033 --> 00:05:34,599
